  "type": "consumable",
  "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg",
  "folder": "fhSubModern00001",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Glossy yellow capsules pressed in someone's apartment kitchen and sold at warehouse parties. The hit lands fast and lasts about as long as the bassline. Quality varies by batch and by who owes who a favor that week.</p><p><strong><em>Desired effects on use.</em></strong> For 1 hour you have advantage on Dexterity (Acrobatics) checks and a +2 bonus to Charisma (Performance) checks.</p><p><strong><em>On use, save against addiction.</em></strong> Make a DC 13 Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, you gain the Addicted condition from Voltbeans (see below).</p><p><strong><em>Addicted from Voltbeans.</em></strong> While you have this Addicted condition, you are also Poisoned and have disadvantage on Constitution saving throws made to maintain concentration.</p><p><strong><em>Withdrawal Modifier: 3.</em></strong> Withdrawal lasts max(3 &minus; your Constitution modifier, 2) long rests, minimum 1.</p>"
    },
